net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.generator
Class GeneratorRegistry

java.lang.Object
  net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.generator.GeneratorRegistry

public class GeneratorRegistry
extends java.lang.Object

Registry for resource generators, which create scripts or CSS data dynamically, as opposed to the usual behavior of reading a resource from the war file. It provides methods to determine if a path mapping should be handled by a generator, and to actually render the resource using the appropriate generator. Path mappings which require generation will use a prefix (preferably one which ends with a colon, such as 'messages:'). Generators provided with Jawr will be automatically mapped.

Author:
Jordi Hernández Sellés, Ibrahim Chaehoi
